column5: TRAVIS TRITT. Been waiting to see him in person for aloooooooooong time, and I got the call. I got tickets to see him this friday at Rama.  Thanks to me Mudder.    And yes,I,ll be taking pics you can count on that.
Right on! That should be a good show!!
Good stuff Brian...enjoy...ya gotta luv them there mudders eh?  Maureen
should be a good show, i got to see him and charlie daniels together at the north dakota state fair about 10 years ago.  what a show they put on.  hope ya have a good time. jason
well say hello to my wife, she will be there too
Saw him in Kansas City a couple of years ago. He's real good. Enjoy the show Brian.
You deserve it Brian! enjoy the show man.
I bet you feel 10 feet tall...
